The paper deals with the problem of classification with minimal annotations and proposes a novel semi-supervised learning framework for deep classification. The paper focuses on improving decision boundaries and features that generalize well, which are key concerns in machine learning and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
